author: tmthyXryn
title: Quick Build
review: I found this at a walmart bin for $1.00 in the US! Incredible, couldn't believe it. Built it immediately once I got home. Loving the Hedwig and a nice little touch to the collection.

author: StevenTheBrick
title: Harry Potter and Hedwig: Owl Delivery
review:
1/5

You're building a table, of course the building experience sucks. The parts are ok, but come in more better sets. There is no playability. The price is meh.
